data.description: Welcome home! Located in the Saddle Creek Ranch neighborhood of Cibolo, this 4 bed 2.5 bath is nearly 2,500 sqft with a 3 car garage. Upon entry you'll immediately notice the tile floors that run throughout the downstairs. To your left you have the formal office space. The living room features a shiplap style accent wall, 9' ceilings, and is open to the dining and room and kitchen . Prepare to be impressed with your new stunning kitchen. Upgraded 42" upper cabinets, granite countertops, stone tile backsplash, reverse osmosis, an island with storage and outlets, and stainless steel appliances. Towards the garage entry you'll find the powder room, closet, and mud space. Upstairs you'll retreat to find the loft space used as an additional living. Spacious secondary bedrooms each with fan fixtures and walk in closets. Utility room is located upstairs for convenience. Secondary bath has plenty of room with double sink vanity with marble countertops and tile floors. The primary suite is roomy with plenty of space for a king size bed. Has tray ceilings, sitting area, and ceiling fan. Primary bath has separate stand up tile shower with dual heads, garden tub, dual sink vanity with marble countertops and sitting area, large walk in, "L shaped" wraparound closet, and private commode. Step out of the French doors to the backyard with covered patio and sun shades. On one of the largest lots in the neighborhood, you have almost a quarter of an acre with the potential for your own outdoor oasis. There is easy access to the new Cibolo HEB Grocery store,  Ft Sam Houston, Randolph AFB, BAMC, restaurants, and shopping. The home feeds to award winning Schertz Cibolo schools. Steele High School has a very strong football program previously winning the State Championship in its short tenure. First-class HOA community amenity center with planned events, junior Olympic-sized pool, basketball court, clubhouse, Shaded children's playscape, workout stations along the walking path and picnic areas.  Additional features include 2" faux wood blinds through out, Pure Wellness whole home water softener, Rain birdIrrigation system, Exterior flood lights, Shed, and extra hose bib.
